  "text": "This study focused on determining the impact of DMPA use on the occurrence of an excessive weight gain because large amount of gaining might lead to overweight and obesity which can further lead to long-term health problems. We used an increasing weight of more than 5 and 10% of their baseline weight at 6 and 12 months after DMPA initiation according to a significant impact on reproductive health when 5-10% of the weight was changed [CITATION_1] [CITATION_2] .",
